TESTIMONIAL_1_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: This app has revolutionized the way I travel. I always know exactly where my flight is and when I need to be at the gate. It's a game-changer!
TESTIMONIAL_2_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: I love how this app keeps me updated on gate changes and delays. It's like having a personal travel assistant in my pocket.
TESTIMONIAL_3_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: As a pilot, I'm impressed with the accuracy of the flight data. It's a must-have for aviation enthusiasts and professionals alike.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: FlightTrack uses real-time data from airlines and airports to provide up-to-date information on flight statuses, delays, and gate changes. Simply enter your flight number or route to get instant updates.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Can I track multiple flights at once?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Yes, FlightTrack allows you to monitor multiple flights simultaneously. You can save and organize your tracked flights for easy access and receive notifications for all of them.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Is FlightTrack available on mobile devices?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Absolutely! FlightTrack is available as a mobile app for both iOS and Android devices. You can download it from the App Store or Google Play Store to track flights on the go.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Does FlightTrack provide historical flight data?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Yes, FlightTrack offers historical flight data for most routes. You can access past flight information, including on-time performance, typical delays, and cancellation rates to help plan future travel more effectively.

FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common questions about our flight tracking service
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How accurate is the flight information?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our flight information is updated in real-time from multiple reliable sources, ensuring high accuracy. However, last-minute changes by airlines may occasionally cause slight discrepancies.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Yes, our application supports tracking of both domestic and international flights across major airlines and airports worldwide.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Is there a mobile app available?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Absolutely! Our flight tracking app is available for both iOS and Android devices, offering the same great features as the web version.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: How far in advance can I track a flight?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: You can track flights up to 24 hours before their scheduled departure time. For some airlines, we may even provide information several days in advance.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Do I need to create an account to use the service?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: While basic flight tracking is available without an account, creating a free account allows you to save favorite routes, receive personalized alerts, and access additional features.
